<b>To redeem your gift card, follow these steps:</b><br />
<br />
1. Visit <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gc">www.amazon.com/gc</a>.<br />
2. Click Apply to Account and enter the claim code when prompted.<br />
3. Gift card funds will be applied automatically to eligible orders during the checkout process.<br />
4. You must pay for any remaining balance on your order with another payment method.<br />
<br />
Your gift card claim code may also be entered when prompted during checkout. To redeem your gift card using the Amazon.com 1-Click&reg; service, 
first add the gift card funds to Your Account.<br />
<br />
If you have questions about redeeming your gift card, please visit <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gc-redeem">www.amazon.com/gc-redeem</a>. 
If you have questions regarding the <b>MyCompany Introductory offer</b>, please contact <b>MyCompany</b>.
